(43, 'Declare a dictionary with the name â€œdaysâ€ where the key is an integer, and the value is a string. Also, initialize this dictionary with keys 1 to 3 corresponding to the days â€œMondayâ€ to â€œWednesdayâ€ (Do not put spacing before or after the colon symbol)\r\n\r\nvar days = [Int:String()] = [________, _________, __________]\r\n', '1:\"Monday\"', '2:\"Tuesday\"', '3:\"Wednesday\"', 7),
